list.comment:
New: delivered DiplomacyEngineAPI for oxp developers
Improvement, code consistency: the Systems and Tax js script now use the API rather than the native engine calls. Improvement, speed: optimized the loops in the engine Improvement, speed: one action per 20 frames Improvement, doc: moved ideas to DiplomacyRoadmap.txt
Bugfix: the init action using the api wasn't working after a restore from the savefile.

task.summary: Added the Diplomacy Engine API. Reimplemented the Systems and Tax script using that API. Probably solved a bug in the Tax script recurrent tax task after a savefile load.
